2026-02-25T20:06:16.9666608Z     [33m        Encoding used to encode the outputfile. Does not apply to output[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9667371Z     [33m        streams. If the encoding is something other than 'bytes' or 'latin1'[39;49;00m
