2026-02-25T20:06:16.9671801Z     [33m    savez_compressed : Save several arrays into a compressed ``.npz`` archive[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9672552Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9672930Z     [33m    Notes[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9673359Z     [33m    -----[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9673945Z     [33m    Further explanation of the `fmt` parameter[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9674668Z     [33m    (``%[flag]width[.precision]specifier``):[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9675373Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9675752Z     [33m    flags:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9676211Z     [33m        ``-`` : left justify[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9676697Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9677218Z     [33m        ``+`` : Forces to precede result with + or -.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9677792Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9678466Z     [33m        ``0`` : Left pad the number with zeros instead of space (see width).[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9679060Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9679274Z     [33m    width:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9679705Z     [33m        Minimum number of characters to be printed. The value is not truncated[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9680185Z     [33m        if it has more characters.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9680472Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9680695Z     [33m    precision:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9681119Z     [33m        - For integer specifiers (eg. ``d,i,o,x``), the minimum number of[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9681570Z     [33m          digits.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9681971Z     [33m        - For ``e, E`` and ``f`` specifiers, the number of digits to print[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9682398Z     [33m          after the decimal point.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9682816Z     [33m        - For ``g`` and ``G``, the maximum number of significant digits.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9683281Z     [33m        - For ``s``, the maximum number of characters.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9683600Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9683817Z     [33m    specifiers:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9684098Z     [33m        ``c`` : character[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9684352Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9684780Z     [33m        ``d`` or ``i`` : signed decimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9685262Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9685574Z     [33m        ``e`` or ``E`` : scientific notation with ``e`` or ``E``.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9685906Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9686164Z     [33m        ``f`` : decimal floating point[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9686448Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9686727Z     [33m        ``g,G`` : use the shorter of ``e,E`` or ``f``[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9687037Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9687268Z     [33m        ``o`` : signed octal[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9687531Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9687783Z     [33m        ``s`` : string of characters[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9688065Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9688322Z     [33m        ``u`` : unsigned decimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9688610Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9688890Z     [33m        ``x,X`` : unsigned hexadecimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9689319Z     [33m[39;49;00m
