2026-02-25T20:06:16.9800698Z     [33m    -----[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9801014Z     [33m    Further explanation of the `fmt` parameter[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9801416Z     [33m    (``%[flag]width[.precision]specifier``):[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9801712Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9801922Z     [33m    flags:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9802184Z     [33m        ``-`` : left justify[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9802442Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9802739Z     [33m        ``+`` : Forces to precede result with + or -.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9803051Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9803426Z     [33m        ``0`` : Left pad the number with zeros instead of space (see width).[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9803805Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9804009Z     [33m    width:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9804429Z     [33m        Minimum number of characters to be printed. The value is not truncated[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9805019Z     [33m        if it has more characters.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9805304Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9805518Z     [33m    precision:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9805937Z     [33m        - For integer specifiers (eg. ``d,i,o,x``), the minimum number of[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9806356Z     [33m          digits.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9806774Z     [33m        - For ``e, E`` and ``f`` specifiers, the number of digits to print[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9807196Z     [33m          after the decimal point.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9807767Z     [33m        - For ``g`` and ``G``, the maximum number of significant digits.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9808244Z     [33m        - For ``s``, the maximum number of characters.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9808560Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9808782Z     [33m    specifiers:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9809054Z     [33m        ``c`` : character[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9809308Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9809581Z     [33m        ``d`` or ``i`` : signed decimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9809882Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9810194Z     [33m        ``e`` or ``E`` : scientific notation with ``e`` or ``E``.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9810534Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9810797Z     [33m        ``f`` : decimal floating point[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9811077Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9811368Z     [33m        ``g,G`` : use the shorter of ``e,E`` or ``f``[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9811675Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9812045Z     [33m        ``o`` : signed octal[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9812305Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9812557Z     [33m        ``s`` : string of characters[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9812834Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9813088Z     [33m        ``u`` : unsigned decimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9813372Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9813643Z     [33m        ``x,X`` : unsigned hexadecimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:16.9813940Z     [33m[39;49;00m
