2026-02-25T20:06:17.0206241Z     [33m    comments : str, optional[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0206837Z     [33m        String that will be prepended to the ``header`` and ``footer`` strings,[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0207402Z     [33m        to mark them as comments. Default: '# ',  as expected by e.g.[39;49;00m
