2026-02-25T20:06:17.0215160Z     [33m    Notes[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0215442Z     [33m    -----[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0215766Z     [33m    Further explanation of the `fmt` parameter[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0216170Z     [33m    (``%[flag]width[.precision]specifier``):[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0216476Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0216686Z     [33m    flags:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0216950Z     [33m        ``-`` : left justify[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0217231Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0217543Z     [33m        ``+`` : Forces to precede result with + or -.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0217862Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0218237Z     [33m        ``0`` : Left pad the number with zeros instead of space (see width).[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0218624Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0218828Z     [33m    width:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0219253Z     [33m        Minimum number of characters to be printed. The value is not truncated[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0219719Z     [33m        if it has more characters.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0220000Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0220212Z     [33m    precision:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0220629Z     [33m        - For integer specifiers (eg. ``d,i,o,x``), the minimum number of[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0221038Z     [33m          digits.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0221437Z     [33m        - For ``e, E`` and ``f`` specifiers, the number of digits to print[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0222037Z     [33m          after the decimal point.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0222472Z     [33m        - For ``g`` and ``G``, the maximum number of significant digits.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0222932Z     [33m        - For ``s``, the maximum number of characters.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0223247Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0223468Z     [33m    specifiers:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0223744Z     [33m        ``c`` : character[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0223996Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0224272Z     [33m        ``d`` or ``i`` : signed decimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0224567Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0224879Z     [33m        ``e`` or ``E`` : scientific notation with ``e`` or ``E``.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0225363Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0225621Z     [33m        ``f`` : decimal floating point[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0225897Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0226187Z     [33m        ``g,G`` : use the shorter of ``e,E`` or ``f``[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0226623Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0226848Z     [33m        ``o`` : signed octal[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0227109Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0227361Z     [33m        ``s`` : string of characters[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0227632Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0227902Z     [33m        ``u`` : unsigned decimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0228180Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0228452Z     [33m        ``x,X`` : unsigned hexadecimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0228747Z     [33m[39;49;00m
