2026-02-25T20:06:17.0342296Z     [33m    Further explanation of the `fmt` parameter[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0342689Z     [33m    (``%[flag]width[.precision]specifier``):[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0342989Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0343194Z     [33m    flags:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0343461Z     [33m        ``-`` : left justify[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0343718Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0344013Z     [33m        ``+`` : Forces to precede result with + or -.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0344327Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0344687Z     [33m        ``0`` : Left pad the number with zeros instead of space (see width).[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0345390Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0345604Z     [33m    width:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0346027Z     [33m        Minimum number of characters to be printed. The value is not truncated[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0346491Z     [33m        if it has more characters.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0346765Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0346981Z     [33m    precision:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0347401Z     [33m        - For integer specifiers (eg. ``d,i,o,x``), the minimum number of[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0347824Z     [33m          digits.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0348226Z     [33m        - For ``e, E`` and ``f`` specifiers, the number of digits to print[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0348652Z     [33m          after the decimal point.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0349073Z     [33m        - For ``g`` and ``G``, the maximum number of significant digits.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0349543Z     [33m        - For ``s``, the maximum number of characters.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0349989Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0350209Z     [33m    specifiers:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0350487Z     [33m        ``c`` : character[39;49;00m
