2026-02-25T20:06:17.0352880Z     [33m        ``o`` : signed octal[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0352973Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0353128Z     [33m        ``s`` : string of characters[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0353216Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0353376Z     [33m        ``u`` : unsigned decimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0353464Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0353633Z     [33m        ``x,X`` : unsigned hexadecimal integer[39;49;00m
