2026-02-25T20:06:17.0739509Z     [33m    savez : Save several arrays into an uncompressed ``.npz`` archive[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0740067Z     [33m    savez_compressed : Save several arrays into a compressed ``.npz`` archive[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0740237Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0740420Z     [33m    Notes[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0740606Z     [33m    -----[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0740968Z     [33m    Further explanation of the `fmt` parameter[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0741294Z     [33m    (``%[flag]width[.precision]specifier``):[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0741463Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0741656Z     [33m    flags:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0741892Z     [33m        ``-`` : left justify[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0742055Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0742407Z     [33m        ``+`` : Forces to precede result with + or -.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0742586Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0743252Z     [33m        ``0`` : Left pad the number with zeros instead of space (see width).[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0743435Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0743634Z     [33m    width:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0744168Z     [33m        Minimum number of characters to be printed. The value is not truncated[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0744439Z     [33m        if it has more characters.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0744607Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0744802Z     [33m    precision:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0745416Z     [33m        - For integer specifiers (eg. ``d,i,o,x``), the minimum number of[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0745617Z     [33m          digits.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0746076Z     [33m        - For ``e, E`` and ``f`` specifiers, the number of digits to print[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0746336Z     [33m          after the decimal point.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0746961Z     [33m        - For ``g`` and ``G``, the maximum number of significant digits.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0747313Z     [33m        - For ``s``, the maximum number of characters.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0747473Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0747671Z     [33m    specifiers:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0747901Z     [33m        ``c`` : character[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0748061Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0748436Z     [33m        ``d`` or ``i`` : signed decimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0748607Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0748985Z     [33m        ``e`` or ``E`` : scientific notation with ``e`` or ``E``.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0749145Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0749418Z     [33m        ``f`` : decimal floating point[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0749586Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0749911Z     [33m        ``g,G`` : use the shorter of ``e,E`` or ``f``[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0750072Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0750312Z     [33m        ``o`` : signed octal[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0750406Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0750552Z     [33m        ``s`` : string of characters[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0750641Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0750805Z     [33m        ``u`` : unsigned decimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0750894Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0751065Z     [33m        ``x,X`` : unsigned hexadecimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0751158Z     [33m[39;49;00m
