2026-02-25T20:06:17.0867923Z     [33m    -----[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0868856Z     [33m    Further explanation of the `fmt` parameter[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0869738Z     [33m    (``%[flag]width[.precision]specifier``):[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0870232Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0870753Z     [33m    flags:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0871402Z     [33m        ``-`` : left justify[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0871886Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0872570Z     [33m        ``+`` : Forces to precede result with + or -.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0872991Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0874358Z     [33m        ``0`` : Left pad the number with zeros instead of space (see width).[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0874989Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0875523Z     [33m    width:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0876265Z     [33m        Minimum number of characters to be printed. The value is not truncated[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0876430Z     [33m        if it has more characters.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0876523Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0876640Z     [33m    precision:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0876914Z     [33m        - For integer specifiers (eg. ``d,i,o,x``), the minimum number of[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0877028Z     [33m          digits.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0877280Z     [33m        - For ``e, E`` and ``f`` specifiers, the number of digits to print[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0877425Z     [33m          after the decimal point.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0877662Z     [33m        - For ``g`` and ``G``, the maximum number of significant digits.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0877859Z     [33m        - For ``s``, the maximum number of characters.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0877949Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0878070Z     [33m    specifiers:[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0878197Z     [33m        ``c`` : character[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0878294Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0878485Z     [33m        ``d`` or ``i`` : signed decimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0878576Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0878800Z     [33m        ``e`` or ``E`` : scientific notation with ``e`` or ``E``.[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0878889Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0879044Z     [33m        ``f`` : decimal floating point[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0879140Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0879322Z     [33m        ``g,G`` : use the shorter of ``e,E`` or ``f``[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0879410Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0879540Z     [33m        ``o`` : signed octal[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0879633Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0879782Z     [33m        ``s`` : string of characters[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0879877Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0880044Z     [33m        ``u`` : unsigned decimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0880131Z     [33m[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0880303Z     [33m        ``x,X`` : unsigned hexadecimal integer[39;49;00m
2026-02-25T20:06:17.0880397Z     [33m[39;49;00m
